OL,3,CWelfare cuts: 'It is going to change
OL,4,Cmy life even more for the worst'
OL,6,FThe possibility of losing personal
OL,7,Findependence payments will cause "a
OL,8,Flot of damage" and change his life
OL,9,F"even more for the worse", a man
OL,10,Fliving with epilepsy has said.
OL,12,FIt comes after changes were announced
OL,13,Fwhich included tightening the
OL,14,Feligibility criteria for the benefit,
OL,15,Fknown as Pip, and scrapping the
OL,16,Fcontroversial work capability
OL,17,Fassessment.
