OL,3,CWelfare cuts: 'It is going to change
OL,4,Cmy life even more for the worst'
OL,6,FGed Higgins, a former recovery truck
OL,7,Fdriver said his "life changed
OL,8,Fovernight" after suffering a seizure
OL,9,Fcaused by epilepsy four years ago.
OL,11,F"I went to bed, fell asleep on the
OL,12,Fcouch, and hours later, I wake up in
OL,13,Fmy living room, I've got paramedics,
OL,14,Fmy daughter and ex-wife around me," he
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,F"I didn't know where I was, what was
OL,18,Fgoing on, and I had just been told
OL,19,Fthat I had a seizure."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
