OL,3,CWelfare cuts: 'It is going to change
OL,4,Cmy life even more for the worst'
OL,6,F"I need that (Pip) for appointments,
OL,7,Fdoctors appointments, to go shopping."
OL,9,FRachel Reeves, Chancellor of the
OL,10,FExchequer, confirmed in the
OL,11,FGovernment's Spring Statement that
OL,12,Fwelfare benefits will be cut by #4.9bn
OL,13,Fon Wednesday 26 March.
OL,15,FThe Government insists that the cuts
OL,16,Fwill ensure the welfare system is
OL,17,F"sustainable" in future and are also
OL,18,Fpart of efforts to get people back to
OL,19,Fwork.
