OL,3,CWelfare cuts: 'It is going to change
OL,4,Cmy life even more for the worst'
OL,6,FBut some backbench Labour MPs have
OL,7,Faccused Reeves of using the cuts to
OL,8,F"balance the books on the backs of
OL,9,Fdisabled people".
OL,11,FGed said that losing his Pip payment
OL,12,Fwould cause "a lot of damage" for him
OL,13,Fas he would "struggle to get about".
OL,15,F"I have got a good family, and I have
OL,16,Fgot a good daughters but they have got
OL,17,Ftheir own lives as well so if I have
OL,18,Fgot an important appointment, I don't
OL,19,Fknow how I would get there," he said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
