OL,3,CWelfare cuts: 'It is going to change
OL,4,Cmy life even more for the worst'
OL,6,F"I'm not playing victim and saying
OL,7,Fthat the world is against me, I'm just
OL,8,Fsaying how my life is.
OL,10,F"I know what that feeling is like
OL,11,Fwhere you're cornered and there's
OL,12,Fnothing else you can do. My life
OL,13,Fchanged over night, in a blink of an
OL,14,Feye.
OL,16,F"They are changing everything and I
OL,17,Fdon't know what that is going to be
OL,18,Flike for me. It is going to change my
OL,19,Flife even more for the worst and that
OL,20,Fis basically how I have felt."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
