OL,6,FA debt advice service in Manchester
OL,7,Fsays it is receiving three times the
OL,8,Famount of calls it normally has since
OL,9,Fthe Government announced welfare
OL,10,Freform.
OL,12,FMoney Wellness in Stretford says plans
OL,13,Fto make fewer people eligible for
OL,14,Fbenefits could hit poorer people the
OL,15,Fhardest.
OL,17,FRebecca Lamb, Money Wellness, said:
OL,18,F"There are a lot of extremely worried
OL,19,Fpeople about how the changes are going
OL,20,Fto impact them."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
