OL,4,Cmy life even more for the worst'
OL,6,FShe added: "There are a lot of
OL,7,Fcustomers that are struggling to
OL,8,Fsleep, that all consumed by debt and
OL,9,Fit's a really difficult time for
OL,10,Fpeople."
OL,12,FThe Government announced that it is
OL,13,Fputting #1billion to support people
OL,14,Finto getting back into work, but to
OL,15,Fprotect the vulnerable, but Rebecca
OL,16,Fhas said that "any changes that the
OL,17,Fgovernment choose to make need to
OL,18,Fensure that those that are financially
OL,19,Fvulnerable aren't made to struggle any
OL,20,Ffurther."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
